PRICE REDUCED TO SELL!  Seller is Motivated. 
Welcome Home to this exquisite two-story Craftsman house nestled in the heart of the picturesque community of Providence Village. 
Providence Village offers residents a variety of amenities including a resort-style community, clubhouse, fitness center, tennis court, pools, fishing ponds, walking trails, parks, playgrounds, tennis & basketball courts and more all within walking distance.
